### EduPortal API - Scheduling Controller
### Calendar and availability management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/scheduling
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### STUDENT CALENDAR & AVAILABILITY
### ===========================================

### Get Student Weekly Calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Student Availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Student Availability - (Admin, Kayitci, Öğrenci)
POST {{baseUrl}}/student/availability
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "14:00",
  "endTime": "18:00",
  "isRecurring": true
}

### Delete Student Availability - (Admin, Kayitci, Öğrenci)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/student/availability/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Student Lessons
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### TEACHER CALENDAR & AVAILABILITY
### ===========================================

### Get Teacher Weekly Calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/teacher/1/calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Teacher Availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/teacher/1/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Teacher Availability - (Admin, Kayitci, Öğretmen)
POST {{baseUrl}}/teacher/availability
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "teacherId": 1,
  "dayOfWeek": 2,
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00",
  "isRecurring": true
}

### Delete Teacher Availability - (Admin, Kayitci, Öğretmen)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/teacher/availability/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Teacher Lessons
GET {{baseUrl}}/teacher/1/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### MATCHING & LESSON SCHEDULING
### ===========================================

### Find Matching Slots (All days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/match?studentId=1&teacherId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Find Matching Slots (Specific day)
GET {{baseUrl}}/match?studentId=1&teacherId=1&dayOfWeek=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Lesson Schedule - (Admin, Kayitci)
POST {{baseUrl}}/lesson
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "teacherId": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "14:00",
  "endTime": "15:00",
  "startDate": "2024-09-02",
  "isRecurring": true
}

### Cancel Lesson - (Admin, Kayitci)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lesson/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

